Open Terminal and enter the following:

1. cd /Applications/Sublime\ Text\ 2.app/Contents/MacOS/
2. edit file ->> “vim Sublime\ Text\ 2″
3. change to hex mode ->> “:$!xxd”
4. find and replace ->> “:%s/5BE509C33B020111/5BE509C32B020111/g”
